<rss xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/" version="2.0"><channel><title>The Far Side - Daily Dose - The Far Side</title><link>https://www.thefarside.com/</link><description>Daily The Far Side - Daily Dose comic strip by Gary Larson from The Far Side</description><atom:link href="https://comiccaster.xyz/feeds/farside-daily.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><category>The Far Side</category><category>Comic Strips</category><docs>http://www.rssboard.org/rss-specification</docs><generator>python-feedgen</generator><language>en</language><lastBuildDate>Sat, 27 Jun 2026 08:21:45 +0000</lastBuildDate><ttl>1440</ttl><item><title>The Far Side - 2026-06-27 #2</title><link>https://www.thefarside.com/2026/06/27/1</link><description>&lt;div style="text-align: center; max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://comiccaster.xyz/.netlify/functions/proxy-farside-image?url=https%3A%2F%2Ffeatureassets.amuniversal.com%2Fassets%2F74805ea0d0ea0137c64d005056a9545d" alt="The Far Side comic" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;"/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 10px; font-style: italic;"&gt;“I’ve warned you kids about this—now I’m gonna straighten you out once and for all.”&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 0.9em;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.thefarside.com/"&gt;Visit The Far Side&lt;/a&gt; | © Gary Larson&lt;/p&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.thefarside.com/2026/06/27/1</guid><pubDate>Sat, 27 Jun 2026 08:11:00 -0400</pubDate></item><item><title>The Far Side - 2026-06-27 #1</title><link>https://www.thefarside.com/2026/06/27/0</link><description>&lt;div style="text-align: center; max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://comiccaster.xyz/.netlify/functions/proxy-farside-image?url=https%3A%2F%2Ffeatureassets.amuniversal.com%2Fassets%2F6f8af6e0d0be0137c62c005056a9545d" alt="The Far Side comic" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;"/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 10px; font-style: italic;"&gt;“What are you gonna tell your dad, Chuck?”&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 0.9em;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.thefarside.com/"&gt;Visit The Far Side&lt;/a&gt; | © Gary Larson&lt;/p&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.thefarside.com/2026/06/27/0</guid><pubDate>Sat, 27 Jun 2026 08:10:00 -0400</pubDate></item><item><title>The Far Side - 2026-06-26 #5</title><link>https://www.thefarside.com/2026/06/26/4</link><description>&lt;div style="text-align: center; max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://comiccaster.xyz/.netlify/functions/proxy-farside-image?url=https%3A%2F%2Ffeatureassets.amuniversal.com%2Fassets%2Fa5c1f5f0d19e0137c68e005056a9545d" alt="The Far Side comic" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;"/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 10px; font-style: italic;"&gt;Carmen Miranda’s family reunion&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 0.9em;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.thefarside.com/"&gt;Visit The Far Side&lt;/a&gt; | © Gary Larson&lt;/p&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.thefarside.com/2026/06/26/4</guid><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jun 2026 08:09:00 -0400</pubDate></item><item><title>The Far Side - 2026-06-26 #4</title><link>https://www.thefarside.com/2026/06/26/3</link><description>&lt;div style="text-align: center; max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://comiccaster.xyz/.netlify/functions/proxy-farside-image?url=https%3A%2F%2Ffeatureassets.amuniversal.com%2Fassets%2F7a40be5002810138d7bb005056a9545d" alt="The Far Side comic" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;"/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 10px; font-style: italic;"&gt;Suddenly, everything froze. Only the buzzing of the tsetse flies could be heard. The crackling grass wasn’t Cummings returning to camp after all, but an animal who didn’t like to be surprised.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 0.9em;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.thefarside.com/"&gt;Visit The Far Side&lt;/a&gt; | © Gary Larson&lt;/p&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.thefarside.com/2026/06/26/3</guid><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jun 2026 08:08:00 -0400</pubDate></item><item><title>The Far Side - 2026-06-26 #3</title><link>https://www.thefarside.com/2026/06/26/2</link><description>&lt;div style="text-align: center; max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://comiccaster.xyz/.netlify/functions/proxy-farside-image?url=https%3A%2F%2Ffeatureassets.amuniversal.com%2Fassets%2Fe3911d90d0c40137c631005056a9545d" alt="The Far Side comic" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;"/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 10px; font-style: italic;"&gt;“I’m leaving you, Frank, because you’re a shiftless, low-down, good-for-nothing imbecile … and, might I finally add, you have the head of a chicken.”&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 0.9em;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.thefarside.com/"&gt;Visit The Far Side&lt;/a&gt; | © Gary Larson&lt;/p&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.thefarside.com/2026/06/26/2</guid><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jun 2026 08:07:00 -0400</pubDate></item><item><title>The Far Side - 2026-06-26 #2</title><link>https://www.thefarside.com/2026/06/26/1</link><description>&lt;div style="text-align: center; max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://comiccaster.xyz/.netlify/functions/proxy-farside-image?url=https%3A%2F%2Ffeatureassets.amuniversal.com%2Fassets%2F7f85dbb0d0ea0137c64d005056a9545d" alt="The Far Side comic" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;"/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 10px; font-style: italic;"&gt;“Hey, everyone! Simmons here just uttered a discouraging word!”&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 0.9em;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.thefarside.com/"&gt;Visit The Far Side&lt;/a&gt; | © Gary Larson&lt;/p&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.thefarside.com/2026/06/26/1</guid><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jun 2026 08:06:00 -0400</pubDate></item><item><title>The Far Side - 2026-06-26 #1</title><link>https://www.thefarside.com/2026/06/26/0</link><description>&lt;div style="text-align: center; max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://comiccaster.xyz/.netlify/functions/proxy-farside-image?url=https%3A%2F%2Ffeatureassets.amuniversal.com%2Fassets%2F99595a20e6f90137ce50005056a9545d" alt="The Far Side comic" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;"/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 10px; font-style: italic;"&gt;“Good heavens, John! Call someone! ... The entire basement looks dry!”&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 0.9em;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.thefarside.com/"&gt;Visit The Far Side&lt;/a&gt; | © Gary Larson&lt;/p&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.thefarside.com/2026/06/26/0</guid><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jun 2026 08:05:00 -0400</pubDate></item><item><title>The Far Side - 2026-06-25 #5</title><link>https://www.thefarside.com/2026/06/25/4</link><description>&lt;div style="text-align: center; max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://comiccaster.xyz/.netlify/functions/proxy-farside-image?url=https%3A%2F%2Ffeatureassets.amuniversal.com%2Fassets%2Ff01cbc50fa830137d52f005056a9545d" alt="The Far Side comic" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;"/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 10px; font-style: italic;"&gt;“Wait a minute! Say that again, Doris! … You know, the part about ‘If only we had some means of climbing down.’”&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 0.9em;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.thefarside.com/"&gt;Visit The Far Side&lt;/a&gt; | © Gary Larson&lt;/p&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.thefarside.com/2026/06/25/4</guid><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jun 2026 08:04:00 -0400</pubDate></item><item><title>The Far Side - 2026-06-25 #4</title><link>https://www.thefarside.com/2026/06/25/3</link><description>&lt;div style="text-align: center; max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://comiccaster.xyz/.netlify/functions/proxy-farside-image?url=https%3A%2F%2Ffeatureassets.amuniversal.com%2Fassets%2F37a71fe0e6f90137ce50005056a9545d" alt="The Far Side comic" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;"/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 10px; font-style: italic;"&gt;Fish funerals&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 0.9em;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.thefarside.com/"&gt;Visit The Far Side&lt;/a&gt; | © Gary Larson&lt;/p&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.thefarside.com/2026/06/25/3</guid><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jun 2026 08:03:00 -0400</pubDate></item><item><title>The Far Side - 2026-06-25 #3</title><link>https://www.thefarside.com/2026/06/25/2</link><description>&lt;div style="text-align: center; max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://comiccaster.xyz/.netlify/functions/proxy-farside-image?url=https%3A%2F%2Ffeatureassets.amuniversal.com%2Fassets%2F777eb650d0ea0137c64d005056a9545d" alt="The Far Side comic" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;"/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 10px; font-style: italic;"&gt;“Seems like Gramp’s been there forever—fossilized right there on his favorite rock. … Scares the hell out of the dog.”&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 0.9em;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.thefarside.com/"&gt;Visit The Far Side&lt;/a&gt; | © Gary Larson&lt;/p&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.thefarside.com/2026/06/25/2</guid><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jun 2026 08:02:00 -0400</pubDate></item><item><title>The Far Side - 2026-06-25 #2</title><link>https://www.thefarside.com/2026/06/25/1</link><description>&lt;div style="text-align: center; max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://comiccaster.xyz/.netlify/functions/proxy-farside-image?url=https%3A%2F%2Ffeatureassets.amuniversal.com%2Fassets%2Ffa235150fa830137d52f005056a9545d" alt="The Far Side comic" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;"/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 10px; font-style: italic;"&gt;“Uh-oh, Lorraine ... someone seems to be checking you out.”&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 0.9em;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.thefarside.com/"&gt;Visit The Far Side&lt;/a&gt; | © Gary Larson&lt;/p&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.thefarside.com/2026/06/25/1</guid><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jun 2026 08:01:00 -0400</pubDate></item><item><title>The Far Side - 2026-06-25 #1</title><link>https://www.thefarside.com/2026/06/25/0</link><description>&lt;div style="text-align: center; max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://comiccaster.xyz/.netlify/functions/proxy-farside-image?url=https%3A%2F%2Ffeatureassets.amuniversal.com%2Fassets%2Faad94c20d0be0137c62c005056a9545d" alt="The Far Side comic" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;"/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 10px; font-style: italic;"&gt;“Now just hold your horses, everyone. … Let’s let it run for a minute or so and see if it gets any colder.”&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 0.9em;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.thefarside.com/"&gt;Visit The Far Side&lt;/a&gt; | © Gary Larson&lt;/p&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.thefarside.com/2026/06/25/0</guid><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jun 2026 08:00:00 -0400</pubDate></item></channel></rss>